        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:326:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/475/606",
        "text": [
          "٤٧٥. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): الْقَنَاعَةُ مَالٌ لَا يَنْفَدُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "475. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Contentment is a wealth that does not exhaust."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2065,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:326:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/475/607",
        "text": [
          "قال السيد الرضي: وقد رَوى بعضُهم هذا الكلام عن النبی (صلى الله علیه وآله)."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "as-Sayyid ar-Raḍī says: Some people have related that this is the saying of the Messenger of Allāh, peace be upon him and his descendants."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
